quran[8{c,v,t}:
12,23,"jis aurat ke ghar mein woh tha woh uss par dooray daalnay lagi aur aik roz darwazay band kar ke boli"" aa ja"" yousuf ne kaha"" khuda ki panah, mere rab ne to mujhe achi manzilat bakhsh ( aur mein yeh kaam karoon! ) aisay zalim kabhi Falah nahi paaya karte """
12,24,"woh uss ki taraf barhi aur yousuf bhi is ki taraf barhta agar apne rab ki Burhan nah dekh laita aisa howa, taakay hum is se badi aur be hiyai ko daur kar den, Dur haqeeqat woh hamaray chuney hue bundon mein se tha"
12,25,"aakhir-kaar yousuf aur woh agay peechay darwazay ki taraf bhage aur is ne peechay se yousuf ka kameez ( khech kar ) phaar diya darwazay par dono ne is ke shohar ko mojood paaya usay dekhte hi aurat kehnay lagi,"" kya saza hai is shakhs ki jo teri ghar wali par niyat kharab kere? iss ke siwa aur kya saza hosakti hai ke woh qaid kya jaye ya usay sakht azaab diya jaye """
12,26,"yousuf ne kaha"" yahi mujhe phansnay ki koshish kar rahi thi"" is aurat ke apne kunba walon mein seshakhs ne ( qareene ki ) shahadat paish ki ke"" agar yousuf ka kameez agay se phataa ho to aurat sachhi hai aur yeh jhoota"
12,27,"aur agar is ka kameez peechay se phataa ho to aurat jhooti hai aur yeh sacha """
12,28,"jab shohar ne dekha ke yousuf ka kameez peechay se phataa hai to is ne kaha"" yeh tum aurton ki chalakiyan hain, waqai barr y ghazab ki hoti hain tumhari chaalein"
12,29,"yousuf, is muamlay se dar guzar kar aur ae aurat, to apne qasoor ki maffi maang, to hi asal mein khata car thi """
12,30,"shehar ki aurtain aapas mein charcha karne lagen ke"" Aziz ki biwi apne nojawan ghulam ke peechay pari hui hai, mohabbat ne is ko be qaboo kar rakha hai, hamaray nazdeek to woh Sarih ghalti kar rahi hai """
